## Broadcasting

The 2023 NHL Stadium Series was broadcast nationally in the United States by [ABC](/NHL_on_ABC) and streamed on [ESPN+](/ESPN%2B). In Canada, the game was simulcast via [Sportsnet](/NHL_on_Sportsnet). The decision to air the game on ABC, rather than ESPN as originally planned, highlighted the growing prominence of NHL games on major broadcast networks.